Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:44.36,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(240,0)}难解疑案频接踵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:51.74,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(240,0)}奇想妙解豁然开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.74,0:00:59.00,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(0,240)}柳暗花明又一村
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.71,0:01:04.71,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(240,0)}往日何曾思明日
